divs: Sighting Detailsmy mother was visiting Captiva island in the gulf. she and her boyfriend were walking and she took a picture of some trees. they didn't see anything but when she looked at the picture the strange object appeared in the frame. she took the picture with a digital camera she has had for about a year. no other pictures had any strange objects. they all came out fine. she took other pictures on the walk but i couldn't see anything on any other photo they took that day. the first photo is the original and the other two are of the photo zoomed in closer. in between the two smallest circles you can make out several dots. i don't if it's a ufo, a camera problem or something natraul but it looks very strange to everyone who sees it. thanks for your time and feel free to contact me .
